items.name: EVEN_ODD
desc: Fill every area, where, when traveling along a line, an uneven number of intersections with polygon edges have happened.

items.name: NON_ZERO
desc: Fill every area, where, when traveling along a line, the summed winding number (that is, -1 for a counter-clockwise-oriented polygon, and +1 for a clockwise-oriented) is non-zero.
